properties.media:imagetext:
Welcome Nhoard
To Start
On Transcontinental Flights, We Offer a Selection
of Hors d'Oeuvre at Cocktail Time.
Salad
On Flights West, We Feature Athenian Salad with Fresh
Garden Greens, Greek Olives, Feta Cheese and Tomato
Wedge. Oil and Vinegar Dressing.
On Eastbound Flights, Crisp Greens and Colorful Vegetables
are Served with Our Dressing of the Day.
Desserts
INTERNATIONAL CHEESE AND CRACKERS
FROM THE PATISSERIE
For Westward Travelers; Our German Chocolate Tart
with Pecans and Coconut in a Pastry Crust.
Passengers Flying East Will Enjoy Our Zabaglione Trifle
with a Marsala Flavored Custard.
Entrée Selections
BRISKET OF BEEF KENSINGTON
Choice Beef Slices in a Mellow English-Style Horseradish
Cream Sauce. Parslied Potatoes, Peas and Carrot Slices.
CHICKEN NORMANDY
Boneless Breast of Chicken Baked in Pan Gravy with
Apple Cider. Green Beans and a White, Wild Rice Blend.
Trans World Specialies
We Have the Enviable Opportunity to Discover Cuisines
from Around the World, and You Are Invited to Share
Some of Our All Time Favorites. Your Flight Attendant
Will Advise You of Today's Selection.
LASAGNA VERDI AL FORNO BOLOGNESE
Sauce Bolognese, Ricotta Cheese and Ground Italian
Sausage Nested between Layers of Spinach Noodles.
FISH AND CHIPS
A British Favorite.
Served with Malt Vinegar Flavored Tartar Sauce.
BAVARIAN WURST PLATTER
COFFEE FLAVORS OF THE WORLD at $1.50 Each
The Perfect Touch of Hot Coffee and Whipped
Cream, It's the Spirit that Makes the Difference!
Jamaican with Kahlua
Rovale with Cognac
Roma with Galliano
Grilled Bratwurst and Knockwurst with a Mustard Glaze.
Hot German Potato Salad and Weinkraut.
THAI BEEF CURRY
Tidbits of Choice Beef in a Curry Sauce with Coconut Juice,
Tomato Bits, Mango Chutney and Strips of Red Ginger.
Please accept our apologies if your choice is not available on today's flight.
D-95
15
